{"tid":1393102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔撚好on99咁支持解放軍啦","createTime":"2019-08-01T03:35:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T03:41:47.000Z","uid":59570,"like":5,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9869bdcbb729348f6bc04ec22ea11703cec614ca","tid":1393102,"uid":59570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:35:00.000Z","msg":"你遊行支持解放軍係咩意思？<br />\n<br />\n國際間一陣真係以為你地真心支持解放軍，<br />\n<br />\n就唔會理香港既事<br />\n<br />\n唔該唔好智障，香港既底牌唔係單純解放軍入城<br />\n<br />\n而係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">解放軍屠城呀</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你地比黑警扑撚到個腦傻左呀？<br />\n<br />\n你估解放軍好過黑警好撚多咩，咪柒比人帶風向啦傻鳩"},{"pid":"5616721ee5a53f2328895a1a9450b939946abec3","tid":1393102,"uid":59570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:35:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"765df4176925e89584e2510f15127a4dd39a53b5","tid":1393102,"uid":59570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:36:06.000Z","msg":"8月5號。  三罷"},{"pid":"4da8106f0c6e8c79c7593e31558d7820b3b49d6e","tid":1393102,"uid":59570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:36:16.000Z","msg":"8月5號。  三罷"},{"pid":"8252d971bf02069a71b295d0e0e7ae0845384cd9","tid":1393102,"uid":59570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:36:39.000Z","msg":"8月5號。  三罷"},{"pid":"689f298d916f9e330f889c55fe1cd35bc93e62a5","tid":1393102,"uid":59570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:36:49.000Z","msg":"8月5號。  三罷"},{"pid":"f2a8f1879216309ffaa2d4ddc458c894a82a5881","tid":1393102,"uid":59570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:36:59.000Z","msg":"8月5號。  三罷"},{"pid":"ba799a7ad80d76f4eb2265f68afdf0c9a85d2651","tid":1393102,"uid":59570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:37:09.000Z","msg":"8月5號。  三罷"},{"pid":"ab99b8661d3e8600e9a3c7811740df05fa1331ad","tid":1393102,"uid":59570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"